README for Sanji Controller
===========================

INTRODUCTION

  Sanji Framework is kind of a IoT integration framework which build on
  MQTT message queue and RESTful API interface to be accessed.

  Sanji Controller is the controller of Sanji Framework,
  since it is implemented based on MVC software architecture.

INSTALLATION

  1) Edit ./build/compile.mk to choose the right architecture.

  2) Get into directory ./build
  
  3) make

